high_descs: Move across the room to the black trash bin that is on the right side of the door.
Pick up the egg out of the trash can.
Move across the room to the sink.
Put the egg in the sink and turn the water on to clean it.  Pick up the egg.
Move across to the room to the microwave.
Place the egg inside the microwave to cook it.
anns.task_desc: Take egg out of trash to rinsed off in the sink to be cooked in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, move around the counter to the trash can on the right.
Pick up the egg in the trash can.
Bring the egg around the kitchen to the sink on the right.
Wash the egg in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned egg to the microwave on the left.
Put the cleaned egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, then go around the wall clockwise until you come to the black wastebasket.
Get the egg out of the wastebasket.
Turn right and go counterclockwise around the room to the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Turn to the microwave on your left.
Put the egg into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed egg into the microwave.
